## Calculating Repeated-Measures ANVOA

-   $F = \frac{MS_{Time}}{MS_{Error}}$

-   $MS_{Time} = \frac{SS_{Time}}{df_{Time}} = \frac{SS_{Time}}{(k - 1)}$

-   $MS_{Error} = \frac{(SS_{W} - SS_{Subject})} {df_{Error}} = \frac{(SS_{W}\ - SS_{Subject})}{(n-1)\times(k-1)}$

